        "excerpt": "# Bulgaria AI coding competitor scan\n\n**Date:** 2026-05-27  \n**Analyst:** Cursor agent  \n**Confidence:** medium-high  \n**Scope:** Bulgarian businesses and Bulgaria-localized providers for AI coding, vibe coding, agentic coding, Cursor/Copilot training, and adjacent AI upskilling.\n\n## Summary\n\nThe Bulgarian market already has direct competition for Vibe Coders Academy. SoftUni is the clearest direct competitor: it has a dedicated SoftUni AI brand, a Vibe Coding / AI-first programming pathway, developer courses for Copilot, Cursor, Claude Code, and an AI Agents and Workflows course covering n8n, LangChain, and LangGraph. NobleProg Bulgaria is the strongest corporate-training competitor for Copilot, Cursor, and agent workflows. Telerik Academy competes for professional developer upskilling with a polished GenAI for Developers sprint. IT STEP, Advance Academy, Aula.bg, and New Horizons are adjacent competitors that can absorb beginner, productivity, and corporate AI training demand.\n\n## Offer & positioning\n\n| Competitor | Directness | Offer & positioning | Audience | Priority |\n|------------|------------|----------------------|----------|----------|\n| SoftUni AI / SoftUni | Direct | La…",
